pt-further-link (2.0.0-1) buster; urgency=medium

  * Rename exec endpoint to run-py
  * Use same output data object for extra IO system as stdout and stderr
  * Execute python as pi user if available
  * Handle output by bytes rather than by line
  * Use asyncio over threads to improve development and performance

 -- Angus Whitehead <angus@pi-top.com>  Fri, 03 Mar 2020 15:04:08 +0000

pt-further-link (1.2.0-1) buster; urgency=medium

  * Added env var FURTHER_LINK_WORK_DIR to override temp file location
  * Added IPC system for handling alternative output types
  * Improved server performace & fixed potential thread memory leak
  * Refactored stopping & cleanup to handle edge cases
  * Added basic events logging

 -- Angus Whitehead <angus@pi-top.com>  Mon, 13 Jan 2019 17:19:23 +0000

